WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:15.180
Balik Pilipinas na ang ilang kapamilya stars na naki-party sa ASAP England tulad ng Bini na Booked and Busy ngayong September at si James Reid na BBW sa teleserye matapos ang pitong taon.

2
00:00:15.630 --> 00:00:25.030
Binigyang pagkilala naman ang ilang bituin ng ABS-CBN sa Gawad Buhay Awards dahil sa kanilang Galing sa Musical.

3
00:00:25.360 --> 00:00:27.580
Nagpapatro, Ganiel Krishnan.

4
00:00:30.270 --> 00:00:40.930
Fresh from ASAP England, excited na si James Reid na sumabak sa teleserye kung saan makakasama for the first time si Asia's superstar Katherine Bernardo sa ilalim ng Dreamscape Entertainment.

5
00:00:41.560 --> 00:00:44.960
I'm very excited and very blessed.

6
00:00:46.580 --> 00:00:51.280
Grabe yung support and I haven't even started shooting yet so very grateful.

7
00:00:51.280 --> 00:00:56.040
Thank you so much to everyone who's supporting and I can't wait to work with Katherine.

8
00:00:56.510 --> 00:00:59.910
Pag-ami ni James, noon pa man gusto na niya makatrabaho si Katherine.

9
00:01:00.150 --> 00:01:07.870
Actually, it's something that I've wanted to do for a while so I'm very grateful I get to work with Katherine.

10
00:01:08.440 --> 00:01:11.380
She's extremely talented so it should be great.

11
00:01:11.670 --> 00:01:18.640
Pitong taon na ang lumipas mula ng huling teleserye ni James kaya't aminado siya na may halong pressure ang pagbabalik taping.

12
00:01:19.340 --> 00:01:24.680
It's very new again. I'm still getting used to it.

13
00:01:24.680 --> 00:01:27.160
There's always pressure but pressure is good.

14
00:01:27.680 --> 00:01:30.480
You know, it means people have high expectations.

15
00:01:30.480 --> 00:01:32.160
It means people expect a lot.

16
00:01:32.160 --> 00:01:33.560
It means everyone's very excited.

17
00:01:34.600 --> 00:01:36.560
Aarangkada na ang taping ngayong Setiembre.

18
00:01:37.350 --> 00:01:48.350
It's my first time working with another leading lady so I'm trying to just give it my best, give it my all and then see what happens, hope for the best.

19
00:01:49.410 --> 00:01:54.090
Samantala, binigyan ng citation ng ilang kapamilya stars para sa kanilang performances sa musical.

20
00:01:54.680 --> 00:01:59.200
Kabilang si Alexa Ilacad, sinakatanggap ng citation para sa female lead performance.

21
00:01:59.200 --> 00:02:01.620
In a musical, para sa liwanag sa dilim.

22
00:02:02.020 --> 00:02:04.520
Si Nikki Valdez naman, para sa next to normal.

23
00:02:04.990 --> 00:02:09.150
Kilig pa rin po talaga ako. To be recognized, it's such an honor already.

24
00:02:09.150 --> 00:02:11.039
It's such a big deal for me as an artist.

25
00:02:11.440 --> 00:02:21.760
Nung ginagawa ko po yung liwanag sa dilim, I was just really doing it out of pure love and enjoyment and for the craft talaga. So parang bonus po talaga ito.

26
00:02:21.860 --> 00:02:28.080
I was in tears. Happy tears that is. I'm just grateful.

27
00:02:29.140 --> 00:02:34.960
And for me, it was the best way to welcome the first day of this month.

28
00:02:36.570 --> 00:02:39.830
Busy naman ang Nations Girl Group BINI sa pag-arangkada ng ber months..

29
00:02:40.180 --> 00:02:46.800
Dadalhin ng walo ang saya sa Visayas at Mindanao matapos ang sold out na BINIVERSE at MINIVERSE events sa Metro Manila.

30
00:02:47.300 --> 00:02:56.620
Opisyal na sisimula ng regional events ng MINIVERSE fanmeet para sa mga little grooms at BINIVERSE fanmeet sa September 28 sa Limketkai Atrium sa Cagayan de Oro.

31
00:02:56.830 --> 00:03:01.030
Magpapatuloy ang saya sa October 12 sa Grand Xing Imperial Hotel sa Iloilo. .

32
00:03:01.580 --> 00:03:04.680
Ngayon pa lang, sold out na ang BINIVERSE fanmeet.

33
00:03:04.710 --> 00:03:06.170
Ganiel Krishnen, ABS-CBN News.

